comments: Warren (IND) makes clean contact with the ball during the inbounds pass.
Barrett (NYK) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Warren (IND) while setting the screen.
Robinson (NYK) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Warren's (IND) while setting the pick.
Warren (IND) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Morris Sr.'s (NYK) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in Payton's (NYK) path during the pick and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Warren (IND) makes brief contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) but does not restrict his FOM.
Randle (NYK) is firming up and make marginal contact with Warren (IND) while setting the screen.
Robinson (NYK) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Warren (IND) while setting the screen.
As Warren (IND) fights over the screen he engages with Robinson (NYK) and restricts his FOM as he attempts to roll to the basket.
Turner (IND) makes "high-five" contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Turner (IND) makes clean contact with Randle's (NYK) shot attempt at the rim.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes incidental contact with Warren's (IND) head during his upward shooting motion.
Holiday (IND) makes marginal contact with Robinson (NYK) as he sets the screen, any contact between Robinson and Sabonis (IND) is deemed incidental.
Barrett (NYK) has two hands around Sabonis (IND) in the post and affects his FOM.
Barrett (NYK) briefly places a hand to the front of Lamb (IND) during the drive.
Robinson (NYK) makes marginal contact with Sabonis' (IND) arm during the rebound.
Sabonis (IND) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) during the pick.
Warren (IND) initiates marginal contact to Morris Sr. (NYK) but does not affect his ability to contest the shot.
Payton (NYK) makes incidental contact with Holiday (IND) after he releases the pass.
Turner (IND) blocks Robinson's (NYK) shot attempt, any additional contact to Robinson on the follow through is deemed incidental.
Holiday (IND) makes contact to the arm of Randle (NYK) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
